(
<figureCitation id="130F2A575C93FF3748FEFCB9FEFCFC82" box="[159,306,870,895]" captionStart="FIGURE19" captionStartId="137.[151,250,1889,1911]" captionTargetBox="[242,1342,231,1826]" captionTargetId="figure@137.[201,1386,193,1868]" captionTargetPageId="137" captionText="FIGURE19.Anisepyris: dietrichorum species-group.A–B.Head indorsal profile.A.A.indivisus Santos&amp; Azevedo, 2000;B. A. triangularis Moreira &amp; Azevedo, 2003; C. male mandible in frontal profile; D. Mesosoma in dorsal profile; E–F. Mesopleuronin frontalprofile;franciscanusspecies-group.G–M.Head indorsal profile.G.A.diori sp. nov.; H.A. elendurisp. nov.; I. A.herumori sp. nov.; J. A.anduzei Evans, 1966(♂);K.A.anduzei Evans, 1966 (♀);L. A.brasiliensis Evans, 1966; M. A. elegantulus Evans, 1966." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242301/files/figure.png" pageId="140" pageNumber="141">Figs 19G–M</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="130F2A575C93FF37495CFCB8FE5EFC82" box="[317,400,871,895]" captionStart="FIGURE 20" captionStartId="152.[151,250,1892,1914]" captionTargetBox="[242,1342,233,1828]" captionTargetId="figure@152.[201,1386,195,1870]" captionTargetPageId="152" captionText="FIGURE 20. Anisepyris: franciscanus species-group. A–B. Head in dorsal profile. A. A. franciscanus Evans, 1966; B. A. metallicus Kieffer, 1905; C–D. Female mandible in frontal profile; E. Male mandible in frontal profile; F. Mesosoma in dorsal profile; G–H. Mesopleuron in frontal profile; guianae species-group. I–L. Head in dorsal profile. I. A. carcharothi sp. nov.; J. A. elatani sp. nov.; K. A. cepus Santos &amp; Azevedo, 2008; L. A. guianae Evans, 1966; M. Mesosoma in dorsal profile; megacephalus species-group.N–O.Head in dorsal profile.N. A.amlachi sp. nov.; O. A.durini sp. nov." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/1242303/files/figure.png" pageId="140" pageNumber="141">20A–H</figureCitation>
